desc: Captured on dazzling 35mm color film, the biggest stars of the Grand Ole Opry from the 1950s shine like never before. Filmed live in Nashville, featuring all the names that made the Grand Ole Opry and country music famous: Ernest Tubb, Ray Price, Carter Family, Minnie Pearl, Jimmy Dickens, Jim Reeves, and many more!

layout.text: Grand Ole Opry Stars of The 50s
